The paper deals with network traffic analysis and anomaly detection, which are typical topics in the computer security (cs.CR) and networking (cs.NI) fields. The paper also mentions the use of visualisation tools, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and computer vision (cs.CV) categories. Finally, the paper describes the development of a new methodology, which could be related to data structures (cs.DS) as well.
